<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 16:15:33 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a0200a26cbdc</link><description>&lt;p&gt;高层建筑，低层生活。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Bushes of green and yellow in front of a high-rise facade." height="2000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/6a0200a26cbdc.jpg" width="1126"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 16:15:33 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a01827594b0d</link><description>&lt;p&gt;母亲节在spa的款待。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Mother's Day treat at the spa. " height="2268" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/rrajath/6a01827594b0d.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://rrajath.some.pics"&gt;@rrajath&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 07:17:12 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>婚礼照片</title><link>https://some.pics/6a0172b3db62e</link><description>&lt;p&gt;婚礼照片&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A bright turquoise concrete wall with a single glass window revealing a pegboard display case, a hanging fluorescent light, and a photocopied sign that reads “wedding photos” followed by a phone number. Everything is weathered and shows signs of being unused." height="1704" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/markwyner/6a0172b3db62e.jpg" width="2272"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://markwyner.some.pics"&gt;@markwyner&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 06:09:58 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a0171e71f1a6</link><description>&lt;p&gt;南石大道&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Perspective view of the corner of a smooth, light-colored brick building. A weathered street name “south stone avenue” is painted across a row of bricks with simple lettering. The cross-street name is scarcely readable on the adjacent wall." height="1704" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/markwyner/6a0171e71f1a6.jpg" width="2272"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://markwyner.some.pics"&gt;@markwyner&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 06:06:34 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>绝美天空</title><link>https://some.pics/6a01701b3f5f4</link><description>&lt;p&gt;不过那片天空啊。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Partial view of a giant white metal rooftop sign for Hotel Congress on a bright sunny day with a clear blue sky behind it. The sign houses unlit neon lights tracing the letters. It is perched on metal scaffolding so the letters can float at night." height="1704" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/markwyner/6a01701b3f5f4.jpg" width="2272"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://markwyner.some.pics"&gt;@markwyner&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 05:58:54 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>